To build new units, such as ships, troops or facilities, first locate a system with the appropriate idle manufacturing facility.  Double-click on that system's Manufacturing and Production icon to view the corresponding window. Right-click to the right of the facility from which you wish to build, and select `Build' from the menu.  This will bring up the Build window. Click on the arrow below the default unit to view a complete list of available items.  Select the unit you wish to build and click the check-mark at the bottom of the window to execute your order.